title: Raja
subTitle: Raju and Madhu are forced apart by the latter's elder brothers, leading to increased distance between the two.

title: Gundaraj
subTitle: Ajay and Pooja fall in love and decide to get married. To earn money and get settled, Ajay applies for a job in Bombay, but is framed in a rape case and is imprisoned for four years.

title: Encounter: The Killing
subTitle: Sam Bharucha, a police inspector, often comes across youth gangs creating nuisance in the city. When a young mobster is killed by him during a shootout, he embarks on a mission to find his family.

title: Saajan Ki Saheli
subTitle: Kunti abandons her baby in order to lead a lavish life and marries a rich man. Years later, she realises that her husband is indulging in an affair and is shocked to find out the truth about the girl.

title: Firaaq
subTitle: In the aftermath of Gujarat's violent 2002 riots, victims find their lives changed forever and reel from the deep impact the upheaval left on them.

title: Raj Kumar
subTitle: Rajkumar's mother sets out to oppose his marriage after she finds out that he plans to marry the rival kingdom's princess.

title: Aap Aye Bahaar Ayee
subTitle: Kumar and Rohit, who are childhood friends, soon turn enemies when Kumar molests Rohit's fiancee out of jealousy. She feels unworthy of Rohit and calls off the wedding.

title: Sanam Bewafa
subTitle: Salman and Rukhsar's love brings two warring families face to face, only for tradition, dowry demands and heartbreak to test their fragile bond.

title: Ghar Sansar
subTitle: When Prakash's father dies, he is forced to shoulder the financial responsibilities of his large family. However, his troubles increase when his younger brother leaves him home to join a gang.

title: Soldier
subTitle: After Major Vijay Malhotra's colleagues betray him, he is branded as a traitor and subsequently killed. But his son, Vicky, vows to take revenge on his father's murderers and prove his innocence.

title: Ekkees Tareekh Shubh Muhurat
subTitle: Pandit Girdhari Laal Sharma wants to get his daughter, Radha, married extravagantly but lacks the money for it. He then devises a plan to source the money, unaware of the consequences.

title: Ekkees Tareekh Shubh Muhurat
subTitle: Pandit Girdhari Laal Sharma wants to get his daughter, Radha, married extravagantly but lacks the money for it. He then devises a plan to source the money, unaware of the consequences.

title: Officer Arjun Singh IPS
subTitle: Arjun Pratap Singh, an IPS officer, strives to overcome multiple challenges and embarks on a mission to restore peace in society.

title: Antim Nyay
subTitle: Jay Singh encounters Seema while struggling to seek justice for his deceased father. As the couple attempts to live a happy life, unforeseen circumstances invite more troubles.

title: Prem Kahani
subTitle: Rajesh, an apolitical poet, is in love with Kamini and leads a peaceful life. However, when his brother is killed by the British government, he decides to become a revolutionary and joins the freedom struggle.

title: Raja Saab
subTitle: Upon Prince Pratap's insistence, Rajoo impersonates him in front of Princess Poonam. But the imitation lands him in trouble when she starts falling for Rajoo, unaware of his poor background.

title: Trishul
subTitle: Born out of wedlock, Vijay grows up with deep resentment towards his biological father Raj, a wealthy industrialist who has been leading a comfortable life with his legitimate family in the big city.

title: Aap Beati
subTitle: Geeta and her father undergo several hardships to ensure that Prakash gets an education abroad. However, things take a turn when, upon his return, he marries a rich girl.

title: Juari
subTitle: Rakesh, a young man, is addicted to alcohol and gets involved in gambling and fraud. However, when someone is in need of help, he readily agrees to do what he can.

title: Sindoor
subTitle: Suspecting an extra-marital affair, Vijay, a professor, abandons his wife, Laxmi. However, years later, when he is hurtled back into Laxmi's life through her adopted daughter, things become clearer.

title: Deewaar: Let's Bring Our Heroes Home
subTitle: Haunted by the past, Vijay turns to crime, while Ravi, his younger brother, becomes an honest police officer. Fate pits them against each other when Ravi is sent to nab Vijay.

title: Namak Halaal
subTitle: Arjun, a youngster, works at a hotel owned by Raja and serves him faithfully. However, when he learns about a plot to kill Raja, he decides to save him from harm at any cost.

title: Namak Halaal
subTitle: Arjun, a youngster, works at a hotel owned by Raja and serves him faithfully. However, when he learns about a plot to kill Raja, he decides to save him from harm at any cost.

title: Suhaag
subTitle: Twins Amit and Kishan are separated at birth. However, when their paths cross in the future, together they work their way through and strive to overcome challenges.

title: Gair Kaanooni
subTitle: Police Inspector Kapil Khanna realises that his baby boy has been switched with a girl child by the hospital and files a lawsuit against the owner, Robert Decosta while trying to find his missing son.

title: Krodhi
subTitle: Vicky plans to marry Aarti, but his dreams are crushed when an incident causes her to lose her life. Fuelled by revenge, Vicky finds himself going down a dark path.

title: Chor Ke Ghar Chor
subTitle: Rajkumari Ophelia hires a thug to steal an idol of Devi Maa that brings good luck to its owner. But the goddess soon begins unleashing her wrath, wreaking havoc in the lives of two noble families.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.

title: Dharam Veer
subTitle: Twin brothers separated at birth become best friends, unaware of their bond as siblings. The queen, their mother, becomes the uniting force as they set out to defeat their evil uncle.

title: Daulat
subTitle: Joseph D'souza frames Ghanshyam, an honest employee, for a murder, forcing him to flee from the police and to leave his family behind. Soon, things take a turn as he hatches a plan to destroy Ghanshyam's loved ones.

title: The Great Gambler
subTitle: Jay, an expert in gambling, works for a criminal unaware that he is being used to gain military secrets. When the police discover this, they assign Inspector Vijay, Jay's lookalike, to stop him.

title: Pyar Ishq Aur Mohabbat
subTitle: Yash, Taj and Gaurav fall madly in love with Isha, a beautiful and charming woman. However, Isha is friendly with all three men, unaware of their feelings towards her.

title: Dil Jo Na Keh Saka
subTitle: Jay and Siya, friends since childhood, decide to part ways to pursue their ambitions. However, they discover their true feelings for each other when their paths cross years later.
